  "description": "Adds the ability for copper tools to oxidize as durability goes down.",
  "body": "<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EeQU5Eq.png\" width=\"650\"/>\n</p>\n\n<center>\n  <a href=\"https://billing.sparkedhost.com/aff.php?aff=3073\">\n    <img src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/cmee6m.jpg\" width=\"800\">\n  </a>\n</center>\n\nOxidizing Copper Tools adds tools that oxidize as their durability wears, going from shiny copper to having a green patina! It's a simple way to add more life and story to early game gear. The oxidization gives a clear indicator on how much durability you have left.\n\n<div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between;\">\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/oct\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/R2meelb.png\" width=\"400\"/>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/oxidizing-copper-tool\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qp0TljH.png\" width=\"400\"/>\n  </a>\n</div>\n\n",
